ul.li: Unget char returns char to input stream

div.p: Keywords: SELECT, FROM, WHERE, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE, CREATE, DROP, etc.
Operators: +, -, *, /, =, less, greater, less-eq, greater-eq, not-eq, concat

ol.li: Single quote for strings: apostrophe text apostrophe
Double quote/backtick for IDs: quote table quote or backtick column backtick
Escape quote by doubling: apostrophe it apostrophe apostrophe s apostrophe becomes it-apostrophe-s
